core":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T04:05:45.000Z","msg":"中小企d垃圾老細真係全世界最撚閪"},{"pid":"7993795940cb3bb72c67ac25f578049bec66fc77","tid":218982,"uid":102056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T04:07:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52f956aab6c72b6e9bec96a505aa0a7051d73f1e","tid":218982,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T04:15:20.000Z","msg":"賺大錢時永遠無員工份, 賺錢少左就開員工刀, 香港無論大中細企業既老闆一樣咁仆街"},{"pid":"f760022694ec71f47a78fb03230b989e285aecbc","tid":218982,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T04:28:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賺大錢時永遠無員工份, 賺錢少左就開員工刀, 香港無論大中細企業既老闆一樣咁仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n賺大錢時永遠無員工份<br />\n<br />\n蝕大錢時, 員工都唔駛還債<br />\n<br />\n員工東家唔打, 打西家, 無論賺蝕公司都要固定出糧<br />\n<br />\n有乜仆街?<br />\n<br />\n難道外國唔係咁？"},{"pid":"b2c39c2531e432a9e364a461326e78e887fd3856","tid":218982,"uid":66246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T04:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3381d0d55dccf179a4f92ffe64f9301b56e61d","tid":218982,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T04:44:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賺大錢時永遠無員工份, 賺錢少左就開員工刀, 香港無論大中細企業既老闆一樣咁仆街</blockquote><br />\n香港勞工法咁既水平,<br />\n唔搞班細既唔通搞客咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac7579e07517475a9af6a4126f7e71579a31394","tid":218982,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T04:47:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>賺大錢時永遠無員工份, 賺錢少左就開員工刀, 香港無論大中細企業既老闆一樣咁仆街</blockquote><br />\n香港勞工法咁既水平,<br />\n唔搞班細既唔通搞客咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港勞工法衰9過支那<br />\n支那做滿1年 佢炒你就要賠1個月<br />\n香港做滿2年先得4/3個月老遣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7428efa0990a426442b7817f230c7abe6c1e7015","tid":218982,"uid":54593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite